-- AirAsia Chief Says He's Not Considering Buying Holding in Virgin Atlantic
-- B y   C h o n g   P o o i   K o o n
-- 2010-12-27T06:32:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-27/airasia-chief-says-he-s-not-considering-buying-holding-in-virgin-atlantic.html
AirAsia Bhd. Chief Executive Officer
Tony Fernandes said he has no plans to buy a stake in Virgin
Atlantic Airways Ltd., denying a report by the Sunday Times
yesterday.  He made the comment in a replied mobile text message to
Bloomberg questions today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chong Pooi Koon in Kuala Lumpur at 
 pchong17@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
